<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5254733>
    dc:description "FIGURES 84–87. Cossodes lyonetii, Western Australia. 84. ♂ (ANIC). 85. ♀ (ANIC). 86. Male genitalia, a. ventral view, b. phallus, c. details of phallus (GP H18, ANIC). 87. Female genitalia (GP 18558, ANIC)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5254733/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5254757>
    dc:description "FIGURES 167–172. Distribution Maps, Cossinae. 167. Macrocyttara expressa (), M. pamphaea (⊖). 168. Zyganisus fulvicollis sp. nov. 169. Z. caliginosus. 170. Z. propedia. 171. Z. acalanthis sp. nov. (), Z. cadigalorum (⊖). 172. Cossodes lyonetii." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5254757/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5254719>
    dc:description "FIGURES 40–45. Culama species, male genitalia. Figs 40–41. C. australis. 40. a. lateral projection of transtilla, b. lateral lobe of juxta, c. bulla (GP AK614, CAK). 41. (GP AK615, CAK). Fig. 42. C. anthracica sp. nov. (GP AK604, CAK). Fig. 43. C. crepera (GP AK709, ANIC). Fig. 44. C. dasythrix (GP AK713, ANIC). Fig. 45. C. suffusca sp. nov. (GP AK605, CAK)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5254719/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

